_components._string: HNG DN CHI GAME BU CUA:

_components._string: Bu cua hay l bu cua tm c  l mt tr chi ph bin  Vit Nam. Vi li chi n gin, bt c ai cng c th hc v chi c ngay lp tc.
_components._N$string: Bu cua hay l bu cua tm c  l mt tr chi ph bin  Vit Nam. Vi li chi n gin, bt c ai cng c th hc v chi c ngay lp tc.

_components._string:
- Game bu cua s dng 3 vin xc xc c 6 mt, mi mt s c 1 hnh tng ng vi hnh trn  t cc: Hu  G  Tm  C  Bu  Cua.
   * M u vn chi, cc bn s c 60 giy  t cc (t ti a 3 ca). Sau  h thng s tin hnh tung xc xc. Cc bn s da vo s hnh trn   phn nh thng thua:
   * Nu trng 1 hnh, cc bn s c 1 ln tin cc, trng 2 hnh c 2 ln tin cc, trng c 3 hnh s c 3 ln tin cc.
   * Nu khng trng hnh no, tt nhin BN s mt ton b s tin cc.
